#, python-format
msgid "%s will be updated to version"
msgstr "%s 將被更新為版本"

msgid "(Disable during dual extrusion printing)"
msgstr "（雙頭打印時慎用）"

msgid "(default)"
msgstr "(預設)"

msgid ""
"1. Advanced setting: Use only when necessary (e.g., nozzle/hotend "
"replacement, post-collision, or mechanical zero adjustment)."
msgstr ""
"1、高級設置：僅在必要時使用（例如噴嘴/熱端更換、碰撞后或調整機械零位后等場"
"景）。"

msgid ""
"1. Ensure that all fixed components have been properly removed before "
"proceeding."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"1. For first use, refer to the accompanying diagram to disassemble the fixed "
"components of the X, Y, and Z axes."
msgstr "1、首次使用時，請參閱隨附的快速指南，拆除 X Y 和Z軸上的固定件"

msgid "1. Keep filament dry to prevent print failures and nozzle clogs."
msgstr "1. 保持耗材幹燥可有效避免打印失敗和噴嘴堵塞。"

msgid ""
"1.Please ensure that the <b>Probe Calibrate</b> has been performed!\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"1.請確保<b>探針校準</b>已經完成！\n"
"\n"

msgid "2. Dry filament periodically when humidity exceeds 50%."
msgstr "2. 建議在濕度高於50%的環境中對耗材進行定期幹燥。"

msgid ""
"2. Follow the image guide strictly during calibration to avoid damaging the "
"vision module or causing print errors."
msgstr ""
"2、如需校準請嚴格按照上圖示例操作，否則將會造成視覺模組損壞或打印異常等問題。"

msgid ""
"2. Once the disassembly is complete, click the 'Next' button to proceed."
msgstr "2、拆卸完成後，點擊 '下一步' 按鈕繼續操作"

msgid ""
"2. Press the 'Raise Platform' button to lift the platform and remove the "
"items underneath."
msgstr "2、按下 '升高平臺' 按鈕以提升平臺，並取出下面的物品。"

msgid "2.Please ensure that the <b>XY Calibrate</b> has been performed!"
msgstr "2.請確保<b>XY偏移校準</b>已經完成！"

msgid "24 Hour Time"
msgstr "使用24小時制"

msgid "3. Always set the proper temperature for your filament!"
msgstr "3. 需根據耗材特性設置合適的溫度!"

msgid "3. If you have any questions, please contact customer service."
msgstr "3、如有疑惑請聯系售後支持"

msgid ""
"3. Once the operation is complete, click the 'Finish' button to conclude the "
"process."
msgstr "3、操作完成後，點擊 '結束' 按鈕以結束整個過程。"

msgid ""
"<b>Start the Dual Z offset calibrate?</b>\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"<b>開始雙Z軸偏移校準？ </b>\n"
"\n"

msgid "<b>Start the eddy sensor calibrate?</b>\n"
msgstr "開始渦流傳感器校準？\n"

